"{\"uid\": \"dailypost.ng-2024-04-19-2024-olympics-minister-enoh-affirms-nigerias-readiness-says-nation-due-for-gold-medals\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Published  on  By  Minister of Sports Development, John Enoh has stated the Ministry is committed to seeing Team Nigeria achieve remarkable success at the upcoming 2024 Olympics in Paris.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 187, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 51, \"end\": 60, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Owan_Enoh\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"John Enoh\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Owan_Enoh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Owan_Enoh\"}, {\"begin\": 113, \"end\": 120, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 0.9480361679878335, \"rank\": 0.05481207760508236, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}, {\"begin\": 181, \"end\": 186, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999963877144, \"rank\": 3.612272462532614e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This was disclosed in a statement by Diana-Mary Nsan, S.A. Media to the Minister, on Friday.\", \"from\": 189, \"to\": 281, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Drawing inspiration from past achievements and a vision for the future, the Minister emphasized Nigeria would be aiming for gold in Paris, in like fashion as the nation's heroics at the 1996 Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 283, \"to\": 488, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 379, \"end\": 386, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 0.9480361679878335, \"rank\": 0.05481207760508236, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}, {\"begin\": 415, \"end\": 420, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999963877144, \"rank\": 3.612272462532614e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Like every area of human endeavor, we expect to build upon what we did at the last Olympics.\", \"from\": 490, \"to\": 583, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After Atlanta 1996, the time has come for Nigeria to win at the very least, a gold medal at the Olympics,\\\" remarked Enoh.\", \"from\": 584, \"to\": 705, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 590, \"end\": 602, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1996_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999580688505552, \"rank\": 4.163448726397708e-05, \"text\": \"Atlanta 1996\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1996_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1996_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 626, \"end\": 633, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 0.9480361679878335, \"rank\": 0.05481207760508236, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To fulfill this ambition, the Ministry has established a ministerial podium performance committee dedicated to strategic planning and execution.\", \"from\": 707, \"to\": 851, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This committee, he said, is diligently assessing various sports where Nigeria holds a competitive advantage.\", \"from\": 853, \"to\": 961, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 923, \"end\": 930, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 0.9480361679878335, \"rank\": 0.05481207760508236, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Collaborating closely with the Nigerian Olympic Committee (NOC) and different sports federations, the Ministry is orchestrating comprehensive training programs and coordinating the opening of training camps both locally and internationally.\", \"from\": 963, \"to\": 1204, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 995, \"end\": 1021, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nigerian Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1023, \"end\": 1026, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.9997819404865487, \"rank\": 0.00021810707355470867, \"text\": \"NOC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Minister underscored the collective effort of all stakeholders involved, emphasizing the synergy between the Ministry, NOC, and federations.\", \"from\": 1206, \"to\": 1351, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1330, \"end\": 1333, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.9997819404865487, \"rank\": 0.00021810707355470867, \"text\": \"NOC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Given all we are doing within the Ministry, the NOC and the different federations, we are working very hard to ensure we are competitive enough and represent Nigeria well enough in Paris,\\\" the Minister added.\", \"from\": 1353, \"to\": 1562, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1512, \"end\": 1519, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 0.9480361679878335, \"rank\": 0.05481207760508236, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}, {\"begin\": 1535, \"end\": 1540, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999963877144, \"rank\": 3.612272462532614e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As preparations intensify, Nigeria is poised to showcase its athletic prowess on the global stage and make its mark at the Paris 2024 Olympics.\", \"from\": 1564, \"to\": 1708, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1592, \"end\": 1599, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 0.9480361679878335, \"rank\": 0.05481207760508236, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Through meticulous planning, robust training regimes, and determination, Team Nigeria aims to leave an indelible legacy of sporting excellence.\", \"from\": 1710, \"to\": 1854, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1789, \"end\": 1796, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 0.9480361679878335, \"rank\": 0.05481207760508236, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While some athletes and sports have qualified for the Games, some others are still undergoing the qualification process,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 1855, \"to\": 1986, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Games will take place in the French capital city of Paris, between July 26 and August 11, 2024.\", \"from\": 1988, \"to\": 2087, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2021, \"end\": 2040, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Frenc